name: Feizy Rumi Rug in Paprika / Aqua-4'x6'
description:
The designers of Tracy Porters Poetic Wanderlust and Feizy Rugs have created the ultimate in casual eleganceThe Rumi Collection. Each hand knotted piece is created using a palette of vibrant yarns, which are shorn closely to expose the warp and weft of the rug. These bold designs are then washed to give the distressed, vintage look of an heirloom that has been handed down for generations.

Please note: Because of the rugs construction and its closely-shorn pile, you will be able to see the warp and weft fibers. Where weft fibers are tied on to one another, you will notice a slight irregularity in the foundation of the rug. Please note that this is simply a characteristic of the type of rug, and it is not considered a defect.
product_name: Feizy Rumi Rug in Paprika / Aqua-4'x6'
construction: Hand Knotted In India In An Antique Washed And Closely Shorn Wool Pile.

Each hand knotted piece is created using a palette of vibrant yarns, which are shorn closely to expose the warp and weft of the rug. These bold designs are then washed to give the distressed, vintage look of an heirloom that has been handed down for generations.

Please note: Because of the rugs construction and its closely-shorn pile, you will be able to see the warp and weft fibers. Where weft fibers are tied on to one another, you will notice a slight irregularity in the foundation of the rug. Please note that this is simply a characteristic of the type of rug, and it is not considered a defect.
construction: Hand Knotted In India In An Antique Washed And Closely Shorn Wool Pile.

name: Feizy Rumi Rug in Paprika / Aqua
meta_title: Feizy Rumi Rug in Paprika / Aqua
description:
The designers of Tracy Porters Poetic Wanderlust and Feizy Rugs have created the ultimate in casual eleganceThe Rumi Collection. Each hand knotted piece is created using a palette of vibrant yarns, which are shorn closely to expose the warp and weft of the rug. These bold designs are then washed to give the distressed, vintage look of an heirloom that has been handed down for generations.

Please note: Because of the rugs construction and its closely-shorn pile, you will be able to see the warp and weft fibers. Where weft fibers are tied on to one another, you will notice a slight irregularity in the foundation of the rug. Please note that this is simply a characteristic of the type of rug, and it is not considered a defect.
product_name: Feizy Rumi Rug in Paprika / Aqua
construction: Hand Knotted In India In An Antique Washed And Closely Shorn Wool Pile.

The designers of Tracy Porters Poetic Wanderlust and Feizy Rugs have created the ultimate in casual eleganceThe Rumi Collection. Each hand knotted piece is created using a palette of vibrant yarns, which are shorn closely to expose the warp and weft of the rug. These bold designs are then washed to give the distressed, vintage look of an heirloom that has been handed down for generations.

Please note: Because of the rugs construction and its closely-shorn pile, you will be able to see the warp and weft fibers. Where weft fibers are tied on to one another, you will notice a slight irregularity in the foundation of the rug. Please note that this is simply a characteristic of the type of rug, and it is not considered a defect.
construction: Hand Knotted In India In An Antique Washed And Closely Shorn Wool Pile.

name: Feizy Burke Rug in Atlantic
description: The Burke Collections unique look comes from a technique that combines hand looming and hand knotting. The result is a collection that has a distressed look but still feels luxurious. Color varies in intensity throughout the hand spun viscose yarns and the subtle sheen plays beautifully against the more rustic wool fibers. Thin, flexible and incredibly versatile, these pieces work well in a variety of settings.

Power loomed in cool tones of celadon, ivory and sky, each transitional design lends an air of tranquility to its surroundings.
construction: Power Loomed In Turkey With An Art Silk Pile.

name: Feizy Soma Rug in Red
description: The Soma Collection is a subtle yet elegant grouping of hand loomed monochromatic designs. The combination of faint color gradations and hand carved patterns result in foundation pieces that are easy to work into decor schemes and create textural interest.
construction: Hand Loomed In India With A Blend Of New Zealand And Other Fine Wools.
